node.text: That’s a wrap #dallas! Thank you to all @spearmintrhinod2 for a fantastic weekend and to all who i had the pleasure of meeting over the two days.  Wishing you all continued success and much love! It was my honor to be on your stage ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bridgette on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DEAR GOD THANK YOU FOR TODAY'.

node.text: In the midst of a chaotic life it’s my hope to you passing through my page that life has given you another good day.  Many hugs to you wherever you are…be safe, be well, and thank you for the support. Xoxo Bridgette B.

@maitlandward @deeper_official @clubkayden…it was an honor to make your vision come to life. 🖤🤍
